  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities </strong>:</p><p>         Provide excellent customer service, outspoken</p><p>         Promote sales for branded/luxury watches, jewelry</p><p>         Able to maintain good customer service at all times</p><p>         To assist customers to achieve a satisfying and enjoyable shopping experience</p><p>         To understand the products and know what customers are looking for and  present them in an appropriate      way</p><p>         Must have good communication skills and a good team player</p><p>         To ensure that physical stock levels are in line with the stock held in the  shop</p><p>         To maintain a tidy and clean shop environment</p><p><strong>Requirements</strong>:</p><p>         Able to work weekends, public holidays and shifts</p><p><strong>Part Time Shift</strong>:</p><p>         10 am – 3 pm  or  3 pm – 8 pm</p><p><strong>Hourly Gross Rate</strong>:</p><p>        $12.09</p><p></p>",
